import Constance from "./const"

const Theme = {
    dark: {
      background: Constance.dark_background,
      border: Constance.dark_border,
      backgroundAlt: Constance.dark_backgroundAlt,
      borderAlt: Constance.dark_borderAlt,
      text: Constance.dark_text,
      gold: Constance.dark_gold,
      navigation:Constance.DarkBlue
    },
    light: {
      background: Constance.light_background,
      border: Constance.light_border,
      backgroundAlt: Constance.light_backgroundAlt,
      borderAlt: Constance.light_borderAlt,
      text: Constance.light_text,
      gold: Constance.light_gold,
      navigation:Constance.White
    }
  }
  
  export default Theme
